# Commit messages

Follow the commit convention in **[AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)**: `type: imperative subject` (`feat` / `fix` / `chore` / `docs` / `refactor` / `test` / `ci`), subject < 72 chars, imperative mood, optional body after a blank line.

One-line hint when drafting: `conventional commit, <72 chars, feat/refactor/fix`.
